Code for the "Optimizing Performance" chapter
=============================================

See the setup instructions in `../README.md`

Additional Setup
----------------

Make sure you are running Redis on port 6379 (as described in the
chapter and set in `config/vanity.yml`).

URLs
----

 * http://localhost:3000/designers/sign_in
 * http://localhost:3000/subscriptions/new
 * http://localhost:3000/creations
 * http://localhost:3000/vanity
